{
  "texts": [
    "The 2 -ΔΔCT method was used to normalize rust gene amplification values relative to the Ae.",
    "tauschii elongation factor endogenous control.",
    "PCR conditions.",
    "A 20 µl PCR containing 100 ng of genomic DNA, 1X GoTaq Flexi green buffer, 1.5 mM MgCl 2, 200 µM dNTP, 200 nM primers and 1 unit of Taq polymerase (M829B, Promega) was used for various fragment amplifications.",
    "Primer sequences are shown in Supplementary Table 31."
  ]
}